// // This module calculates the sum and carry output based on three input bits: two significant bits (a and b) and a carry-in (c). The sum output results from the AND operation among the three inputs, while the carry output is generated by evaluating the logical conditions for carry generation using OR and NOT operations.
module top_module(a,b,c,sum,carry);input a,b,c;
output sum,carry;
assign sum=a^b^c;
assign carry=((a^b)&c)|(a&b);
endmodule
